---
title: Bulk Employee Upload Flow
config:
  layout: elk
  look: handDrawn
  theme: dark
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant UI as 🖥️ AddExpenseDetailsManModal
    participant XLSX as 📊 XLSX Library
    participant Validation as ✓ Validation
    participant Supabase as 📡 Supabase
    participant DB as 💾 PostgreSQL
    participant Audit as 📋 Auditlog
    
    User->>UI: 1. Click "Bulk Upload"
    UI-->>User: 2. Show file picker
    User->>UI: 3. Select Excel file
    
    UI->>XLSX: 4. Read file (XLSX.read)
    XLSX->>XLSX: 5. Parse Excel sheets
    XLSX-->>UI: 6. Return JSON array of rows
    
    Note over UI: File loaded<br/>Example: 1000 rows
    
    UI->>Validation: 7. Validate each row
    
    loop For each row (1 to 1000)
        Validation->>Validation: Check required fields
        Note over Validation: • emp_code<br/>• emp_name<br/>• amount<br/>• month
        
        alt Row Valid
            Validation-->>Validation: ✓ Pass
        else Row Invalid
            Validation-->>Validation: ✗ Fail, store error
        end
    end
    
    Validation->>Validation: Calculate stats
    Note over Validation: Valid: 980<br/>Invalid: 20<br/>Total: 1000
    
    alt Errors Found
        Validation-->>UI: Return error report
        UI-->>User: Show validation errors
        Note over User: "20 rows have errors<br/>See error report"
        User->>UI: Fix Excel and retry
    else All Valid
        Validation-->>UI: All rows pass
        
        UI->>Supabase: 8. INSERT bulk_upload_batches
        
        Supabase->>DB: 9. INSERT batch record
        Note over DB: batch_id, file_name,<br/>row_count, status=pending
        
        DB-->>Supabase: 10. Return batch_id
        Supabase-->>UI: 11. batch_id created
        
        UI->>Supabase: 12. INSERT employee_expense_payouts (bulk)
        
        Note over Supabase: INSERT 980 rows in batch
        
        Supabase->>DB: 13. Bulk INSERT with batch_id
        Note over DB: Loop 980 inserts:<br/>emp_code, emp_name, amount,<br/>month, batch_id, status
        
        DB-->>Supabase: 14. All inserts confirmed
        Supabase-->>UI: 15. Bulk operation success
        
        UI->>Audit: 16. logExport(action=BULK_UPLOAD)
        Audit->>Supabase: 17. INSERT into audit_logs
        Supabase->>DB: 18. INSERT audit record
        DB-->>Supabase: 19. Confirmed
        
        UI->>Supabase: 20. UPDATE bulk_upload_batches
        Supabase->>DB: 21. SET status=completed
        DB-->>Supabase: 22. Updated
        
        UI->>UI: 23. Close modal
        UI-->>User: 24. Show success
        Note over User: "Successfully uploaded 980 rows<br/>Batch ID: xyz123"
        
        User->>User: 25. Navigate to ExpenseRecordsView
        User->>User: 26. See new payouts in list
        
        Note over Supabase: === REAL-TIME UPDATES ===
        
        DB->>DB: 27. Broadcast 980 INSERT events
        Supabase->>Supabase: 28. Batch process events
        Supabase-->>UI: 29. Emit aggregated update
        UI->>UI: 30. Refresh expense records table
        UI-->>User: 31. New records visible
    end
    
    rect rgba(100, 149, 237, 0.2)
    Note over DB: === ROLLBACK SCENARIO ===
    Note over DB: If validation fails for all rows,<br/>no batch is created, no inserts happen
    end
    
    style User fill:#1e40af,stroke:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style UI fill:#059669,stroke:#10b981,color:#fff
    style XLSX fill:#7c3aed,stroke:#a78bfa,color:#fff
    style Validation fill:#dc2626,stroke:#f87171,color:#fff
    style Supabase fill:#ea580c,stroke:#fb923c,color:#fff
    style DB fill:#d97706,stroke:#fbbf24,color:#fff
    style Audit fill:#b91c1c,stroke:#fca5a5,color:#fff
